			</div>
			<div class="skills-table-row">
				<span><a href="https://github.com/nearform/lastlight/blob/main/skills/security-feedback/SKILL.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><code>security-feedback</code></a></span>
				<span>Process a maintainer's comment on a security scan issue — break findings into actionable issues or record accepted risks in <code>SECURITY.md</code>.</span>
			</div>
			<div class="skills-table-row">
