		<p class="section-note">All skill files live in the <a href="https://github.com/nearform/lastlight/tree/main/skills" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><code>skills/</code></a> directory; the build cycle's role prompts (<code>architect</code>, <code>executor</code>, <code>reviewer</code>) live in <a href="https://github.com/nearform/lastlight/tree/main/workflows/prompts" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><code>workflows/prompts/</code></a>. The agent personality is defined in <a href="https://github.com/nearform/lastlight/blob/main/agent-context/soul.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><code>agent-context/soul.md</code></a>.</p>
